OL,3,CNorthern Ireland students make cut at
OL,4,Cfilm awards
OL,6,FA group of talented schoolchildren
OL,7,Ffrom Belfast have picked up the Best
OL,8,FFilm (age 12-15) prize at the
OL,9,Fprestigious Into Film Awards in London.
OL,11,FThe pupils from Park School on
OL,12,FRavenhill Road made their film
OL,13,FSuperhero School over four months with
OL,14,Fthe help of the Into Film team and hit
OL,15,Fthe red carpet in Leicester Square on
OL,16,FTuesday.
OL,18,FThey were presented with their award -
OL,19,Fin the 12 to 15 group age category, by
OL,20,FIrish actor, director, writer and
OL,21,Fproducer Sharon Horgan.
