OL,6,FPupil Sofia gave the group's
OL,7,Facceptance speech.
OL,9,F"We feel really proud and happy. We
OL,10,Fwant to say a big thank you to Into
OL,11,FFilm for giving us the chance to be
OL,12,Fcreative," she said.
OL,14,FMeanwhile St Colmcille's High School
OL,15,Fin Crossgar was named filmmaking
OL,16,Fchampions at the ceremony for their
OL,17,Fefforts to integrate filmmaking across
OL,18,Fthe curriculum.
