OL,6,FThe awards received a record number of
OL,7,Fentries from across the UK this year.
OL,8,FHugh Grant and Geri Halliwell-Horner
OL,9,Fwere among the stars presenting awards.
OL,11,FPark School in Belfast is a co-
OL,12,Feducational school for children with
OL,13,Fmoderate learning difficulties.
OL,14,FTeacher Jon McKinley, who organises
OL,15,Fthe school's filmmaking activities,
OL,16,Fsaid the inspiration for the film came
OL,17,Ffrom real-life experiences.
