OL,3,CNorthern Ireland students make cut at
OL,4,Cfilm awards
OL,6,FTheir winning film is set in a
OL,7,Fsuperhero school where every child has
OL,8,Fa unique power. The story follows a
OL,9,Frivalry between two speed-powered
OL,10,Fstudents Speedy and Quicklight.
OL,12,FPark School Principal Bernie Davis
OL,13,Fsaid the school was "buzzing" with the
OL,14,Fpupils' success.
OL,16,F"It has been fantastic seeing the
OL,17,Fchildren grow. Their self confidence,
OL,18,Fself esteem have grown. I am bursting
OL,19,Fwith pride. It is my proudest moment
OL,20,Fin the thirty years that I have been
OL,21,Fteaching."
